webscript.description:
POSTing one or more email addresses (or even just the domains, if sent without an @) to this webscript to validate those domains<br/>
The Content-Body should have the form:
<pre>
    {
      emails: [<email>, <email>, ...]
    }
</pre>
The response will look like:
<pre>
{
   "domainsChecked":
   [
      "alfresco.com":
      {
         "isValid": true,
         "failureReason": "",
         "failureNotes": ""
      }
      ,
      "gmail.com":
      {
         "isValid": false,
         "failureReason": "PUBLIC",
         "failureNotes": ""
      }
      ...
   ]
}
</pre>
